<title>USA: CCC Information names new president, COO.</title>
<headline>CCC Information names new president, COO.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-07-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>CCC Information Services Group Inc said Wednesday it appointed Githesh Ramamurthy as president and chief operating officer.</p>
<p>Ramamurthy previously served as president of the company's Insurance and Product Development Divisions.  </p>
<p>The position of president and chief operating officer is newly created.</p>
<p>CCC Information supplies software and communications systems to the automotive claims industry.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
